  File     : BUGS  ( Last Audit: 2004.11.29 )
  Project  : Freyja 0.3.5 'Chimera'
  Author   : Terry 'Mongoose' Hendrix II

  Sending Bug reports:
	o Send me your ~/.freyja/Freyja-chimera.log file!
    o Tell me your Linux distrobution or version of your other OS
	o Tell me you graphic card model and windowing system version
	o If you can include library versions
	o I will look at stack traces, etc but they're not needed

  Contact:
	http://icculus.org/freyja		mongoose@icculus.org

 =-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-==-=

 Show Stoppers 
	o Crash on mesh delete for some character models
	o Crash on delete single object ( rare, hard to reproduce )

 Editing
	o Bones recursively adjust on generic rotation
	o Bones react oddly to scaling

 Animation
	o Animation playback removed from this release.
	o Tree for browsing/editing animations ( DnD ) isn't implemented.
	o No vertex morphing animation removed in this release.
	o Matrix palette skinning not supported due to old Egg backend.

 Misc
	o Full disk write fail not reported for screen shot.

